        "body": "<p>You get <code>I/System.out: -1<\/code> because your <code>TextView<\/code> view <strong>not<\/strong> your <code>RelativeLayout<\/code> as Blackbelt commented, does not have an <code>id<\/code>.<\/p>\n\n<p>To get the real id:<\/p>\n\n<ol>\n<li><p>Assign in an id first<\/p><\/li>\n<li><p>and then use <code>textView.getId()<\/code>.<\/p><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n",
